  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How well do you know your video game trivia?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Test your video game knowledge in Video Game Trivia!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Video Game Trivia has never been so much fun. Challenge yourself or have a video game trivia night with friends and family in Party Mode. It comes with the most popular video game categories including Arcade, Atari, Nintendo, Personal Computer, PlayStation, SEGA, and Xbox!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Video Game Trivia includes high quality graphics and covers the most popular categories:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atari</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nintendo</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Personal Computer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PlayStation</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SEGA</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Xbox</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single Player Mode.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party Mode (Up to 4 Players).</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect for Group Trivia Nights.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick, Pick-up-and-Play Sessions.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Family-Friendly Trivia for All Ages.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>So what are you waiting for? Download it now and get your brain ready for Video Game Trivia!</strong></p>",
